2. COMMERCIAL USE
================================================================

"Commercial Use" means any use of the Software that:

  (a) Is performed by or on behalf of a legal entity (company,
      organization, government body) in connection with that entity's
      business operations, products, or services.

  (b) Processes data on behalf of paying clients or customers.

  (c) Generates revenue, directly or indirectly, for the user or
      the user's employer.

Commercial Use of the Software BEYOND the Free tier requires a paid
license ("Pro License" or "Team License") purchased from the licensor
via https://getdatacleaner.com or an authorized reseller.

The Free tier includes:
  - Regex-only PII scanning (unlimited documents, unlimited data size)
  - LLM scanning limited to 500 characters per document
  - Audit log generation
  - CSV, JSON, TXT, and LOG format support

The Pro License additionally unlocks:
  - Unlimited LLM scanning
  - dc scrub-dump command (deterministic database dump anonymization)
  - PDF, DOCX, XLSX, and SQL format processing
  - Programmatic API access
  - SHA-256 deterministic fake value generation
  - Priority email support

